    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
