      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s been meticulously cared for in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
