    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling, this specimen delivers linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure long-term chassis rigidity. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing original-spec Sachs dampers and fresh bushings for that signature tactile feedback. This is a concours-level example with zero oxidation and a flawless service history for the discerning collector.",
